---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import ContentPage from '../components/ContentPage.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Editorial Policy | Pet Care Blog"
  description="Learn about our commitment to providing accurate, trustworthy, and unbiased pet care content."
>
  <ContentPage title="Editorial Policy" updated="February 2026">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-0 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">Our Commitment to Quality Content</h2>
    <p>
      At Pet Care Blog, we are dedicated to providing pet owners with accurate, helpful, and trustworthy information. Our editorial standards ensure that every piece of content meets the highest quality benchmarks.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">Editorial Independence</h2>
    <p>
      Our content is created independently by our team of writers, veterinary consultants, and pet care experts. We maintain complete editorial independence in all our recommendations and advice.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">Research & Accuracy</h2>
    <p>
      Every article published on our site undergoes a rigorous review process to ensure accuracy. Our content is based on:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 my-4 space-y-2">
      <li>Peer-reviewed veterinary research and studies</li>
      <li>Expert input from licensed veterinarians</li>
      <li>Established pet care best practices</li>
      <li>Real-world experience and user feedback</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">Product Reviews Methodology</h2>
    <p>
      When we review products, our evaluations are based on:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 my-4 space-y-2">
      <li>Hands-on testing when possible</li>
      <li>Analysis of product specifications and ingredients</li>
      <li>Comparison with similar products in the market</li>
      <li>Consideration of customer reviews and feedback</li>
      <li>Value assessment relative to price point</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">Our Expert Team</h2>
    <p>
      Our content is created and reviewed by professionals with expertise in:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 my-4 space-y-2">
      <li>Veterinary medicine and animal health</li>
      <li>Pet nutrition and dietary science</li>
      <li>Animal behavior and training</li>
      <li>Pet product evaluation and safety</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">Content Updates</h2>
    <p>
      We regularly review and update our content to ensure it remains accurate and relevant. When significant new research or information becomes available, we update our articles accordingly and note the update date.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">Corrections Policy</h2>
    <p>
      If we discover an error in our content, we correct it promptly and transparently. Readers who identify potential errors are encouraged to <a href="/contact" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">contact us</a> so we can investigate and make corrections if needed.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">Questions?</h2>
    <p>
      If you have any questions about our editorial process or content standards, please <a href="/contact" style="color: var(--color-forest-green);">contact us</a>. We value transparency and are happy to discuss our approach.
    </p>
  </ContentPage>
</BaseLayout>
